		</div>

		<Step 
			image="/hiw-image/beeco4-howitworks-pic4.svg"
			title='Thanks to your actions, '
			greenTitle='everyone will win in the end.'
			paragraph="Fringilla nec odio pellentesque condimentum senectus aliquet sociosqu fames cubilia nostra risus pellentesque nisi platea ad nullam amet curabitur maecenas class aenean."
